      "description": "Presenting an unparalleled example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. It features a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Rigorously inspected to ensure mechanical perfection, this specimen represents a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than absolute refinement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
