      "description": "Hey there! You've really got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it honestly still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like a total dream and has been kept spotless. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
