    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade FD3S RX-7, featuring the iconic 13B-REW power plant with its complex sequential twin-turbocharger setup functioning in perfect harmony. This example maintains its original vacuum routing integrity and exhibits robust, factory-spec compression across both rotors. The chassis remains a masterclass in balance, utilizing its front-midship engine placement and lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension to deliver unparalleled lateral grip. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp five-speed manual gearbox and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Every component, from the R1-spec dual oil coolers to the unblemished interior plastics, reflects a vehicle preserved in a showroom-fresh state, free of the typical heat-cycling degradation found in lesser examples.",
